# Repository-root .gitignore (SPEC-009 Phase B).
#
# Kept minimal on purpose: each app/<stack> already carries its own
# .gitignore for stack-specific build artifacts (app/migrator/.gitignore's
# /migrator binary, app/web/.gitignore's node_modules/dist, app/iac/.gitignore's
# .terraform/*.tfstate) -- this file only covers root-level/cross-stack
# concerns that don't belong to any single stack.

# Local .env files are never committed. All actual commands in this repo
# (root Makefile, .devcontainer/compose.tools.yml, .github/workflows/*.yml)
# reference .devcontainer/versions.env explicitly (`--env-file
# .devcontainer/versions.env` / `include`); they do not rely on Compose's
# default .env auto-load. Callers without an explicit env file (e.g. the VS
# Code Dev Containers extension) are covered by the build.args fallback
# defaults in .devcontainer/compose.tools.yml instead.
.env

# macOS Finder metadata (this repo is developed on macOS; harmless but
# never intentional to track).
.DS_Store

# ISSUE-036: signing key ring files generated by `make auth-signing-keys`.
# These contain RSA private key material and MUST NEVER be committed.
.secrets/
